explanation.summary: Kt qu in tm  cho thy on ST b chnh ln, y l mt du hiu rt quan trng cn c nh gi y t khn cp.
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy on ST (phn sng sau phc b QRS v trc sng T) b nng cao ln r rt so vi ng nn. Theo hng dn y khoa, tnh trng chnh ln on ST l mt du hiu rt quan trng, thng cho thy c tim ang b thiu mu nghim trng, c kh nng do tc nghn mch vnh, c th dn n nhi mu c tim (ST-elevation myocardial infarction - STEMI). Mc d nhp tim ca bn l 63.67 ln/pht v thi gian dn truyn in tim QRS l 0.094 giy u nm trong gii hn bnh thng, nhng du hiu chnh ln on ST l u tin hng u cn c x l.
explanation.recommendations: Bn cn n bnh vin ngay lp tc  c thm khm v iu tr khn cp. Khng nn tr hon, v y c th l du hiu ca mt tnh trng tim mch nguy him.
explanation.next_steps: Tm kim s tr gip y t khn cp (gi cp cu hoc n phng cp cu bnh vin) ngay lp tc. Bc s s thc hin thm cc xt nghim  xc nh nguyn nhn v a ra phc  iu tr ph hp.
